ch.nolix.core.documentNode

Class DocumentNodeoid

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.nolix.core.documentNode.DocumentNodeoid
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Headered
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DocumentNode, SimplePersistentDocumentNode, SubDocumentNode

    public abstract class DocumentNodeoid
extends java.lang.Object
implements Headered
    A DocumentNodeoid can have: -1 header -several attributes that are a DocumentNodeoid themselves The methods of a DocumentNodeoid are not final that they can be overwritten by an implementation with a better performance.
    Author:
    Silvan Wyss
